data.description: Great Ranch-style brick home has 5 bdrms, 2.5 baths,(1 bed in bsmt is conforming) living/dining with fireplace, plus great room on main floor. Main floor master has own 3/4 bath. Huge family room with 2nd fireplace, 4th bed, office, 1/2 bath & laundry in fin. Basement. Hardwood floors under carpet. Fantastic heated SUN ROOM looks out to fenced yard. 2-car attached garage. New roof in July. Good bones. Great neighborhood.
